name: FOOK Token
description: FOOK Token (FOOK) is part of the FOOK Ecosystem. FOOK Token charges a 25% transaction tax that pays holders 23% USDC rewards based on volume, 1% to directly to liquidity, and 1% to marketing and development expenses. The FOOK Ecosystem includes three tokens including FOOK Token (25% tax with USDC rewards), FOOK Five (5% tax with BTC.b rewards), and FOOK Zero (0% Taxes), as well as FOOK Stake, FOOK App, and FOOK Music. FOOK Music is planned for release in late 2023.
